Competitor Analysis|||||||||CR - Compeitor Analysis|||||||||BQ 1 - Analysis Algorithm||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||
Name (#SD)|Competitor Analysis||||||||1|||||2|3||4||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||REF|Identified Semantic APIs
Description|This service domain provides the range of competitor analysis that inform and support product and service design and business development activities and decisions. It draws on external market research and internal business intelligence gathering as necessary. A standard set of analytical views can be defined and maintained as well as targeted ad-hoc analysis as necessary||||||||E|||||E|E||E|I||||||I||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||Triggering
Example of Use|Example of use: A product design unit obtains competitor analysis in order to refine product requirements|CR Competitor Analysis Instance Record|Competitor Analysis Instance Record|||||An analysis that applies a form of algorithm/assessment to research materials in order to develop a competitor viewpoint|IO||||||||O|IO||||||||O|||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||#|Listed Semantic API Descriptions
