Consumer Investments|||||||||CR - Consumer Securities Order Transaction|||||||||BQ 1 - Quote|||||||||BQ 2 - Compliance|||||||||BQ 3 - Funding Check|||||||||BQ 4 - Order Initiation|||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||
Name (#SD)|Consumer Investments||||||||1|2|||||||3|||||||||4|||||||||5|||||||||6||||7|||||8||||||||||||||||||||||||||||REF|Identified Semantic APIs
Description|This supports consumer initiated securities investment and trading activity for their self-managed securities investments. Trades will typically be blocked/netted against the bank's own securities position for subsequent market execution. Quotes/prices are based on the prevailing price at the time of the customer instruction to trade||||||||E|E|||||||E|I||||||||E|I||||||||E|I||||||||E|I|||E|||||E|||||||||||||||||||||||||||||Triggering
