Description|Handle the deployment, execution and on-going refinement of a prospect campaign. This includes many types of proactive prospect acquisition campaigns. The campaign execution process performs the initial selection and confirmation/validation of candidate lists and includes providing critical feedback on the impact of the campaign to the design unit to support re-calibration and refinement of the specification based on practical experience||||||||E|E|E|E||E|E||E|I|E||E|||||E|E|E|||||E||E|IE|E|||||E||E||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||Triggering
