Name (#SD)|Servicing Activity Analysis||||||||1|2||||3|4||5|6||||||7||8|||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||REF|Identified Semantic APIs
Description|Analyze customer servicing position activity, including teller, case/contact center traffic and VoIP activity. Analysis includes captured call/channel/device type, activity, onward routing and resolution decisions for operational and procedural insights and facility/process and training improvement (Root Cause Analysis)||||||||IE|E||||E|E||E|IE||||||IE||E||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||Triggering
