Executive Summary|This service domain analyzes servicing activity to support continual service improvement|||Servicing Activity Type||||The type of servicing activity for which the analysis is performed (e.g. self service, contact center assisted,  ATM access)|IO|IO||||IO|IO||O|IO||||||||O|||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||1|EvCR Initialize servicing root cause analysis
